You consent to our cookies if you continue to use our website.

About
Cookies are small text files that can be used by websites to make a user's experience more efficient.

The law states that we can store cookies on your device if they are strictly necessary for the operation of this site. For all other types of cookies we need your permission.

This site uses different types of cookies. Some cookies are placed by third party services that appear on our pages.

You can at any time change or withdraw your consent from the Cookie Declaration on our website.

Learn more about who we are, how you can contact us and how we process personal data in our Privacy Policy.

Please state your consent ID and date when you contact us regarding your consent.

Jungheinrich Material Handling & Warehouse Solutions

Tailored warehouse solutions for the challenges of Industry 4.0.

Material handling is our passion. At Jungheinrich, we have been using our knowledge and experience to serve customers across all industries since 1953 and we have since become a leading provider of material handling equipment. Efficient internal processes are a decisive factor for the success of companies, and that’s why we’ve made it our aim to offer optimally coordinated material handling concepts that are individually tailored to the requirements of each customer.

Numerous successful partnerships show that we’re on the right track. In our work every day, we are driven to achieve the best solutions with and for our customers.

Individual material handling and warehouse solution concepts for all industries.

Individual solutions instead of standards. Jungheinrich has industry expertise in a wide variety of areas – from logistic, food & beverage, cold store to healthcare. This expertise helps us to develop and implement efficient material handling concepts tailored to the needs of our customers. We have sales and service representatives in 42 countries worldwide who would be happy to help you find the right material handling solutions for your company.

A perfect solution for every application.

With Jungheinrich by your side, you can rely on material handling solutions tailored to your needs for all applications – with perfect coordination between every component. Whether transport, storage or order picking, Jungheinrich will work with you to find the answers to your material handling and warehouse challenges. Thanks to our decades of expertise in logistics processes, interfaces and components, our competence as a systems provider enables seamless optimisation of your warehouse with partial and full automation.

Material handling and warehouse solutions from a single source.

Whether you’re doing a fleet renewal with new forklifts and pallet trucks or looking for high-quality used forklifts and the flexible rental trucks. Whether you want to use racking systems in your warehouse or plan to bring your conveyor technology into the digital age, you can rely on Jungheinrich as a partner. In addition to your purchased equipment, you also benefit from our first-class customer service and comprehensive service network of more than 5,300 technicians working for you worldwide.

Holistic energy competence.

The fact that we combine every component, from the truck to the battery to the charger, makes us unique in the market. Jungheinrich is the only manufacturer that develops and produces controls, software, batteries and charging technology for its trucks. We are continuously expanding this pioneering role as a total solution provider in intralogistics. 95 per cent of our trucks are already electrically powered and highly energy efficient. Jungheinrich also uses innovative technologies such as lithium-ion batteries and energy recovery.
